#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "There are ways to help keep your children away from harm while you are on the move."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Your child will feel reassured knowing you have a plan of action."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 2Ô∏è‚É£ things you can do to ensure that you and your children are as safe as possible when you are travelling in a crisis situation."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 2Ô∏è‚É£ things you can do to ensure that you and your children are as safe as possible when you are travelling in a crisis situation:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **MOVE SAFELY**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 2Ô∏è‚É£ things you can do to ensure that you and your children are as safe as possible when you are travelling in a crisis situation:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Travel with a group of people you know where possible."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If you need to show your passport or ID, try to keep it in your hands."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When it's hard, remember you're trying your best in a difficult situation."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Be sure to look after yourself too."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. You are making a difference to the safety of your children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Human traffickers are people who want to take children away from their families and make money from it. They usually target vulnerable people, like children who are unaccompanied by an adult or are escaping from difficult situations."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Sometimes, children may not realise that they are being tricked by traffickers. They might be scared to report the adult who is threatening them."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ things for you to do to help protect your children from traffickers."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ things for you to do to help protect your children from traffickers: "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **TEACH**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **GET AWAY**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **TALK**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 3Ô∏è‚É£ things for you to do to help protect your children from traffickers:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Traffickers can be anyone - men, women, couples, and even people from your own community."
