#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Teach your children people sometimes lie and try to trick children into coming with them."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Teach children to trust their instincts and get away if something feels strange."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Tell children to talk to a trusted adult if they feel confused or worried."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for joining us. Talking to children about traffickers can be hard for both you and  your children. Remember to be kind and patient with yourself and your children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Being in a shelter can be lonely and stressful for children."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "There are things you already know how to do, like doing daily activities and practising self-care. These can help you and your children feel safe and secure in a new place."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ new tips that will help you to support your children in a shelter."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Press Play ‚ñ∂Ô∏è to learn 3Ô∏è‚É£ new tips that will help you to support your children in a shelter:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1Ô∏è‚É£ **MAKE IT FAMILIAR**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2Ô∏è‚É£ **FIND THE POSITIVE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3Ô∏è‚É£ **REASSURE**"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 3Ô∏è‚É£ new tips that will help you to support your children in a shelter:"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If possible,take a comfort item from home with them to a shelter"
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Decorate the shelter together, with notes or pictures for the walls if you can."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Find something to smile about together. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Share one good thing that happened at the end of each day with your child - no matter how small."
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Try to reassure your children as often as you can. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For younger children, you may want to give them a hug or hold them when they are feeling scared. "
msgstr ""

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For older children, let them know that you are here for them and give them the space to talk to you."
